values:
we're after the same rainbow's end.  wherever you're going, i'm going your way.   two drifters off to see the world,    there's such a lot of world to see. i'm not so sure the world deserves us. ♥

.

if i didn't add you, this is goodbye. ♥
i love being curled up under your sheets, i feel so safe in your arms. ♥

"i went in the ocean, i went looking for some love, all i found is that i found i haven't found enough."
this is all of me, right here; and nothing is able to pick it up. i'm lonesome and all i miss is having someone to curl up with and feel their heart beat, right next to my own. the silence only broken by the whispering of our fingers. i am alone, and was never more aware. good night. ♥.
